cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the application of Information Theory in Machine Learning, specifically in the context of Deep Learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the Information Bottleneck concept, which is a formulation of information extraction based on IT, making cs.IT (Information Theory) another likely category. The applications of IB in deep learning include computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also discusses technical mistakes and problems caused by applying ideas from IT, which is a common issue in neural networks (cs.NE).
